  "body": "<center><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/xbR6jaoJ/images/69e90c573d1d6d20fc112da13889ffdd422d0603.png\" alt=\"A number of rabbits are on a small glass platform and fully dressed in a suit, complete with bow tie, pipe, monocle and top hat. The bow tie and top hat have various colors following Minecraft dyes\" width=\"673\" height=\"360\" /><br/>\nWhat could be better than bunnies? Fancy Dapper Bunnies, of course!\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/xbR6jaoJ/images/b0afcf272df813675735283907e06cb869e9bc89.png\" alt=\"A screenshot of two rabbits wearing a full suit to show a relatively front and rear view of the outfit the mod adds\" width=\"673\" height=\"378\" />\n<br/>\n</center>\n<br/>\nModel by <a href=\"https://twitter.com/RazzleberryFox\">RazzleberryFox</a>. Individual parts of the outfit can be disabled, and rabbits are randomly weighted for fanciness, allowing for many, many different variations!\n<br/>\n<br/>\nMod is client-side only.",
